To Build:

$ gem build vexruby_heap.gemspec

To push to Rubygems.org:

$ gem push vexruby_heap-0.x.x.gem

-------------

Usage:

  require 'rubygems'
  require 'vexruby_heap'

  h = Vex::Heap.new

  h.empty?  # returns true

  h.insert(10)
  h.insert(20)
  h.insert(15)

  h.peek    # returns 20
  h.remove  # returns 20
  h.peek    # returns 15

  h.size    # returns 2
